# Owner "never to production" list (explicit lock)
#   ZZnotforproduction/        -> covered above
#   supabase/migrations/       -> covered by **/supabase/migrations/ above
#   scripts/                   -> covered above (now anchored: /scripts/, /apps/VCSM/scripts/, /apps/VCSM/src/scripts/, /apps/Traffic/src/scripts/)
#   apps/WT/                   -> covered at top of file
